object.script:
function onTick() speed=input.getNumber(1) battery=input.getNumber(2) rps1=input.getNumber(3) rps2=input.getNumber(4) range=input.getNumber(5) track1=input.getNumber(6) track2=input.getNumber(7) speedC=speed/65
end
function onDraw()
screen.setColor(100,100,100) screen.drawTextBox(0,2,64,6,string.format("%.0f",speed).." KPH",0,0)
screen.setColor((speedC)*250,(250)-speedC*250,0) screen.drawRectF(32,10,(speedC*27),5) screen.drawRectF(32,10,(speedC*-27),5)
screen.setColor(50,50,50) screen.drawRect(5,10,54,5) screen.drawRectF(32,10,1,5)
screen.setColor((rps1/13)*250,(250)-(rps1/13)*250,0) screen.drawRectF(4,47,7,-(rps1*2.4))
screen.setColor((rps2/13)*250,(250)-(rps2/13)*250,0) screen.drawRectF(53,47,7,-(rps2*2.4))
screen.setColor(50,50,50) screen.drawRect(4,27,7,20) screen.drawRect(53,27,7,20)
screen.setColor(50,50,200) screen.drawRectF(11,37,4,-(track1*1.3))
screen.setColor(50,50,200) screen.drawRectF(49,37,4,-(track2*1.3))
screen.setColor(50,50,50) screen.drawRect(11,27,4,20) screen.drawRect(49,27,4,20)
screen.drawRectF(11,37,4,1) screen.drawRectF(49,37,4,1)
screen.setColor(80,10,10) screen.drawTextBox(-7,49,32,6,string.format("%.1f",rps1),0,0) screen.setColor(50,50,50) screen.drawTextBox(-2,57,32,6,"T1",0,0)
screen.setColor(80,10,10) screen.drawTextBox(39,49,32,6,string.format("%.1f",rps2),0,0) screen.setColor(50,50,50) screen.drawTextBox(34,57,32,6,"T2",0,0)
screen.setColor(20,20,20) screen.drawRectF(20,40,24,14)
screen.setColor(30,80,30) screen.drawTextBox(20,42,26,6,"range",0,0)
if speed > 3 then screen.drawTextBox(20,48,26,6,string.format("%.0f",range).."km",0,0) else screen.drawTextBox(20,48,26,6,"---",0,0) end
screen.setColor(40,40,40) screen.drawRect(20,40,24,14)
screen.setColor(10,10,10) screen.drawRectF(0,17,64,7)
screen.setColor(80,10,10) screen.drawTextBox(0,18,64,6,"battery "..string.format("%.0f",battery*100).."%",0,0)
end

c = 32
function onTick()
ammo1 = input.getNumber(1) ammo2 = input.getNumber(2) ammo3 = input.getNumber(3)
pitchRad = input.getNumber(4)*400*0.0174533 pivotRad = (input.getNumber(5)*-360+90)*0.0174533
dist = input.getNumber(6)
aim = input.getBool(3)
end
function onDraw()
screen.setColor(250,120,0) screen.drawRect(1,42,20,16) --RA screen.drawTextBox(1,43,20,8,"RA",0,0) screen.drawRect(75,42,20,16) --HA screen.drawTextBox(75,43,20,8,"HA",0,0) screen.drawRect(23,48,50,10) --R screen.drawTextBox(24,49,32,10,"Rocket",0,0)
if dist < 3999 and dist > 1 then screen.drawTextBox(33,1,30,8,string.format("%.0f",dist).."m",0,0) end
screen.setColor(0,200,200) if ammo1 < 1 then screen.setColor(250,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(1,49,20,10,string.format("%.0f",ammo1),0,0) --RA
screen.setColor(0,200,200) if ammo2 < 1 then screen.setColor(250,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(75,49,20,10,string.format("%.0f",ammo2),0,0) --HA
screen.setColor(0,200,200) if ammo3 < 1 then screen.setColor(250,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(57,49,10,10,string.format("%.0f",ammo3),0,0) --R
if aim then screen.setColor(250,0,0,130) screen.drawCircle(48,c,15) screen.drawCircle(48,c,7)
screen.setColor(250,0,0,130) screen.drawLine(48,c-20,48,c+20) screen.drawLine(28,c,68,c) end
screen.setColor(250,0,0,200) screen.drawRect(2,10,10,3) screen.setColor(250,150,0) screen.drawLine(8,12,8+13*math.cos(pitchRad),12-13*math.sin(pitchRad)) screen.setColor(0,200,200,200) screen.drawLine(8,12,16,12) screen.drawLine(8,12,13,6)
screen.setColor(250,0,0,200) screen.drawCircle(82,12,6) screen.setColor(250,150,0) screen.drawLine(82,12,82+10*math.cos(pivotRad),12-10*math.sin(pivotRad))
end
